Arcanine (TCG)

From Bulbapedia, the community-driven Pokémon encyclopedia.
Jump to navigationJump to search
← #0058: Growlithe
Pokémon
#0060: Poliwag →
For Pokémon TCG Pocket cards, see Arcanine (TCG Pocket).

Arcanine has been featured on 36 different cards since it debuted in the Base Set of the Pokémon Trading Card Game. Arcanine cards are normally Fire-type or Fighting-type Stage 1 Pokémon.

List of Pokémon cards featuring Arcanine

Arcanine
Cards listed with a blue background are only legal to use in the current Expanded format.
Cards listed with a green background are legal to use in both the current Standard and Expanded formats.
